data.description: Remarkable, custom built craftsman home situated on a cul-de-sac in desirable neighborhood "The Point" with gorgeous views overlooking the hill country and Canyon Lake. Solid surface floors and upgraded granite throughout. Double sliding glass doors lead you to over 640 sq foot of outdoor living with wood burning fireplace, dining, and a fire pit. Open kitchen, living and dining with floating art niche wall with high end LED Dimplex 50" fireplace. Lots of designer touches and high ceilings. Work out space, multiple living areas, dual dining and panoramic views from the upstairs bonus room. Custom designed bathroom with dual vanities, and a 10 x 6 foot double shower head solid treated glass walk in shower. Double driveways and retaining wall suitable for parking multiple vehicles including space for an RV with 30 amp electric service. 2 AC units, Metal Roof. Refrigerator, washer and dryer convey.
